{
  "text": "We are interested in minimizing the bound of the transfer function T mz\u221e , i.e., find the minimum \u03b3 \u2265 0 such that |T mz\u221e (j\u03c9)| < \u03b3 for all \u03c9 \u2208 R. [CITATION_1] The following result follows from [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
